phrases: Do not hurt Saizo any more!
Does your sadness awaken the power of the Kushimitama?
If he had never met you,
never had anything to do with you,
this never would have happened to Saizo.
Isanami, do not listen to him.
All the other braves should have drawn their last breath by now.
Everyone is so serious about what is going on with Isanami.
Quit running your mouth and fight me!
You are rather tough, are not you?
But you should learn your limits.
Is this where you have been, Princess?
How long are you going to hide in there?
Do you really not want to go to tonight's banquet?
You call it a banquet, but it is a matchmaking meeting, is not it?
The one who likes you would be very sad to hear that.
Most men do not like my red hair or these family tattoos.
Both your tattoos and the color of your hair.
His warm hand reminds me of that time.
I have been looking everywhere for you.
I do not like any of them.
The princess insists she does not wish to go.
How dare you say such a thing, Raizu-sama?
I shall prepare a flower bath for you.
I will get the flowers right away.
I shall take my time and prepare the bath with care.
The water should be just right by the time you return from the banquet.
Just make sure you use roses, okay?
Just as glamorous and boring as usual.
Is everyone really so desperate to get married?
I cannot think of anyone I would want to marry.
But if I did meet someone,
I wonder what he would be like.
Can you imagine, a woman with tattoos?
Is not it a family tradition?
But it is so crude, and her hair is such a dull red.
Not to mention she is scrawny.
It is no wonder no lord is interested in her.
Who cares if I am not popular?
I like my hair and tattoos.
You have no right to talk about me that way.
I have come to retrieve you.
Are you bothered by what those girls said?
They are right about one thing.
I like my hair and tattoos,
but I am not a fan of this thin, unfeminine body.
It is cute in its own right.
I will love you however you are.
Could my soul mate be closer than I thought?
It feels nice to be loved.
I want to stay here forever.
Then you should stay here forever.
You will not laugh at me for not getting married?
In fact, I would be delighted.
I am so comfortable here that I do not want to move.
I will surrender myself to happiness and stay here forever.
I want to stay wrapped up in these forever.
Is that all you have got?
Are you sure you have not lost your edge?
I want to take my time killing you.
I will have to reject your offer.
I do not care what you want.
How does it feel knowing your friends are being erased one by one?
She does not need to answer the question.
We will find out soon enough, will not we?
Do not listen to this freak, Isanami!
You do not have time to worry about others.
No, I want his cold piercing glare.
I want the smell of blood.
He smells of blood and rust and dust.
He has the petrifying gaze of a killer.
The primal rush of killing one another!
That was a disgusting trick, you bastard.
No one has broken my illusion before.
Seduced by a fairyland you have never experienced before,
in the warm embrace of your lover,
deep in a world of happiness until you die.
Where is the pleasure in that?
That lukewarm experience will never give me what I want!
Fighting, short of breath, blood flowing, and mind numb!
Then I will give it to you.
I, Iga Ninja Kuchiba, shall make my move.
I cannot catch anything but small ones.
These would not even be good with drink.
Are you going to catch some for me, Veronica?
By the time you get back, I will...
Nice to meet you, brave number ten.
It is a pleasure to meet you.
I have been looking forward to meeting you.
You are just like he described.
Now we can finally get to know each other.
We will be saying good bye soon.
Why do not we give it a go?
Are you cold on the inside, too?
Sorry, but you cannot beat my spear.
Why are you trying to kill me, anyway?
That is just what that lord said.
I have got nothing to do with it.
I have been ordered to kill all the braves!
Are your orders that important to you?
You are quite a talkative brave, are not you?
Why do not you shut your mouth?
If you are going to keep me quiet, I prefer you use your lips.
After all, we are just a guy and a girl.
I am afraid I cannot do that, even for a woman.
I have got big plans for myself.
What a terrible face you are making.
That is how you have always lived.
It is all for your dream.
I have struggled to survive since I ended up in this country.
To take back my proof of royalty and return to my homeland...
Everything I have done, I did for my dream.
If you want it, let us make a deal.
I have not wavered until now.
I lived only to accomplish my own goals.
Alone in this cold, bloody, dark world.
I never looked for warmth or comfort.
There is no such thing as a cozy home.
You have put up quite a fight, but you cannot win.
The Ice told us everything she knew about your abilities.
Even though she called herself a brave, she hated you all.
It is up to you whether or not you believe me,
but if you think about it, you will understand.
The way you pretend you are a family is disgusting.
I am sure she said something like that.
Isanami, do not listen to him!
Where do you think you are looking?
She joined us when she realized it was a lie.
Those who do not see it are destined to die...
I will not miss this time.
You are an unbelievably pathetic man.
I do not plan to die here.
I have got people and the whole wide ocean waiting for me.
I bet there is plenty of good women out there, too.
Sorry, but you are going to die here.
You cannot tie me down with that!
I do not take orders from anyone!
I will not have anyone force their ideals on me!
The strong will always control the weak.
You think this will kill me?
You know he cannot do that.
Let us not give him false hope.
I promise I will be fine.
It is because I am weak.
Because I cannot fight like everyone else.
Do this, and the power will be yours.
Sasuke, Kakei-san, Rokuro-san, old sea dog,
I will not let your deaths be in vain.
Who are you calling a pervert?!
I did not call you one!
I wish you would have stayed asleep!
The final episode of Brave 10 is The Warrior of Light.
